m-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; bac=
kground-color: #ccc;">  talked</a>=C2=A0about it a <a href=3D"https://link.=
mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30401764.271446/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZX=
JnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMTEtMDMvemlsbG93LWlzLWRvbmUtdHJhZGluZ=
