color: #ccc;">
and did</a>, when=C2=A0Zillow was buying a lot of=C2=A0houses and house pri=
ces were going up. Back in 2021, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusi=
ness.com/click/30401764.271446/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9u=
L2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDktMjgvd2VsbHMtZmFyZ28tc3dhcHBlZC1zb21lLWRpZ2l0cz9jbXB=
