<tr>
<td class=3D"body-header-container" style=3D"border-collapse: collapse; mso=
-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt;">
<h2 style=3D"font-weight: bold; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Arial=
, Helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -1px; font-size: 20px; border-bott=
om-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px =
5px;">1MDB</h2>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In the 2010s, Malaysian government officials w=
anted to steal billions of dollars from their people, so they came to Goldm=
an Sachs Group Inc. for financial structuring advice. <a href=3D"https://li=
nk.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30401764.271446/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21=
iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTgtMTEtMDIvZG9uLXQtc3RlYWwtdGhlLWJyaW=
JlLW1vbmV5P2NtcGlkPUJCRDAxMzAyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX=
3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMDEzMCZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVm=
Zg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBd79bfdfe" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"i=
temscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none =
!important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-=
bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> Goldman obliged</a>: A Goldm=
an team led by Tim Leissner helped structure a series of bond deals in whic=
h a Malaysian entity called 1MDB raised billions of dollars, which was then=
 allegedly stolen by a middleman named Jho Low, who used some of it to pay =
bribes to Malaysian officials, some to pay kickbacks to the Goldman bankers=
,=C2=A0and the rest=C2=A0to buy yachts and art for himself. Goldman itself =
(disclosure: where I used to work) made hundreds of millions of dollars of =
fees on these transactions, a fee rate that was a bit high for underwriting=
 sovereign-linked bonds but pretty normal for underwriting crime.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In the 2020s, a new Malaysian government wante=
d the money back, so they came to Goldman for =E2=80=A6=C2=A0well, for the =
money, but also a little bit for financial structuring advice? We <a href=
=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30401764.271446/aHR0cHM6L=
y93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjAtMDctMjQvZ29sZG1hbi1k=
b2VzLWEtbWFsYXlzaWEtZGVhbD9jbXBpZD1CQkQwMTMwMjNfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXV=
tPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMzAxMzAmdXRtX2NhbXBhaW=
duPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB1468a04a" itemprop=3D"StoryLink"=
 itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-de=
coration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #=
000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  talked in 20=
20</a> about Goldman=E2=80=99s settlement with Malaysia over 1MDB. The basi=
c terms were:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Goldman paid Malaysia $2.5 billion in=
 cash.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Malaysia stood to get a lot=
 of other money back, over time, as authorities untangled the 1MDB situatio=
n: Low and his conspirators allegedly spent their stolen money on a lot of =
assets (yachts, real estate, =E2=80=9CThe Wolf of Wall Street=E2=80=9D movi=
e rights, etc.), and a lot of those assets were seized by governments and w=
ould be returned to Malaysia.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Gold=
man guaranteed that Malaysia would get=C2=A0seized=C2=A0assets=C2=A0worth a=
t least $1.4 billion. If it didn=E2=80=99t, then Goldman would make up the =
difference.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CIn connection with the guarantee,=E2=
=80=9D Goldman said in its <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.c=
om/click/30401764.271446/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29sZG1hbnNhY2hzLmNvbS9tZWRpYS1yZW=
xhdGlvbnMvcHJlc3MtcmVsZWFzZXMvY3VycmVudC9hbm5vdW5jZW1lbnQtMjQtanVseS0yMDIwL=
mh0bWw/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBa92e8e33" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=
=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: =
none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; bo=
rder-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> press release</a>,=C2=
=A0=E2=80=9CGoldman Sachs performed valuation analysis on the relevant asse=
ts and believes based on that analysis that the guarantee does not present =
a significant risk exposure to the firm.=E2=80=9D I wrote at the time:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That last sentence is just gratuitous showing =
off, isn=E2=80=99t it? =E2=80=9COur Stolen Assets Valuation Group modeled t=
hese assets and concluded that they have at least a 95% chance of being wor=
th more than the $1.4 billion put that we wrote against them.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Honestly, they financial-engineered their sett=
lement for doing financial-engineering crimes, it is so Goldman. =E2=80=9CW=
e are better at evaluating and pricing and hedging weird financial risks th=
an our counterparties are,=E2=80=9D is the basic message here, =E2=80=9Cso =
we will take on those risks, at the right price.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Well! Now there=E2=80=99s a valuation dispute.=
 Bloomberg=E2=80=99s=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.co=
m/click/30401764.271446/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGV=
zLzIwMjMtMDEtMzAvbWFsYXlzaWEtcG0tYW53YXItdGVsbHMtZ29sZG1hbi10by1wYXktdXAtb2=
4tMW1kYi1zZXR0bGVtZW50P2NtcGlkPUJCRDAxMzAyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09Z=
W1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMDEzMCZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249=
bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB96126773" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" it=
emscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decor=
ation: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000=
000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">Anisah Shukry and=
 Michelle Jamrisko report</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Malaysian Prime Minister Anwar Ibrahim demande=
d that Goldman Sachs Group Inc. honor its settlement with the government fo=
r its role in the 1MDB scandal, saying the Wall Street firm shouldn=E2=80=
=99t use its financial strength to dictate terms. =E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The settlement announced in July 2020 called f=
or Goldman Sachs to pay $2.5 billion while guaranteeing the return of $1.4 =
billion of 1MDB assets seized by authorities around the world, in exchange =
for Malaysia dropping charges against the bank.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Goldman must also make a one-time interim paym=
ent of $250 million if Malaysia has not received at least $500 million in a=
ssets and proceeds by August 2022, according to the bank. However, the two =
disagree over whether the government had received the $500 million in proce=
eds by the August deadline, Goldman Sachs said in a filing last year.=C2=A0=
</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Here is the filing, <a href=3D"https://link.ma=
il.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30401764.271446/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9p=
eD9kb2M9L0FyY2hpdmVzL2VkZ2FyL2RhdGEvODg2OTgyLzAwMDA4ODY5ODIyMjAwMDAwMi9ncy0=
yMDIyMDkzMC5odG0/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBcc0a2965" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" =
itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-dec=
oration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #0=
00000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> Goldman=E2=80=
=99s 10-Q for September 2022</a>, in a section on =E2=80=9Cother financial =
guarantees=E2=80=9D:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Other financial guarantees also in=
clude a guarantee that the firm has provided to the Government of Malaysia =
that it will receive, by August 2025, at least $1.4 billion in assets and p=
roceeds from assets seized by governmental authorities around the world rel=
ated to 1Malaysia Development Berhad, a sovereign wealth fund in Malaysia (=
1MDB). In connection with this guarantee, the firm is also required to make=
 a one-time interim payment of $250 million towards the $1.4 billion if the=
 Government of Malaysia has not received at least $500 million in assets an=
d proceeds by August 2022. The firm considers the reports that it receives =
on a semi-annual basis, expected in February and August, in evaluating the =
progress of Malaysia=E2=80=99s recovery efforts. In the latest report as of=
 August 2022, the Government of Malaysia unilaterally reduced the value of =
one asset previously included in its prior reports by $80 million and decli=
ned to include substantial additional assets in its accounting of assets an=
d proceeds recovered. The firm and the Government of Malaysia disagree abou=
t, and continue to discuss, whether the Government of Malaysia did, in fact=
, recover at least $500 million as of August 2022 and whether any interim p=
ayment was due. =E2=80=A6 Any amounts paid by the firm would, in any event,=
 be subject to reimbursement in the event the assets and proceeds received =
by the Government of Malaysia through August 18, 2028 exceed $1.4 billion.<=
/p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I guess the situation here is that if Malaysia=
 seizes a yacht from a 1MDB conspirator, Goldman can say =E2=80=9Cgreat, th=
at=E2=80=99s a $200 million yacht, we=E2=80=99re going to count that agains=
t our guarantee,=E2=80=9D and Malaysia can say =E2=80=9Cwhat are you talkin=
g about, that=E2=80=99s a $120 million yacht, tops, you still owe us the mo=
ney,=E2=80=9D and then they go to arbitration. And obviously both sides are=
 biased here, in a pretty direct way. And, sure, maybe Goldman=C2=A0<em>is=
=C2=A0</em>better at the pricing and risk management of these assets, and a=
t making valuation arguments to arbitrators, so perhaps it has an advantage=
. On the other hand Malaysia has the advantage that its argument is =E2=80=
=9Ccome on Goldman Sachs, give us back the money that you helped to steal,=
=E2=80=9D and it=E2=80=99s hard for=C2=A0Goldman to look=C2=A0<em>great=C2=
=A0</em>in this arbitration. Shukry and Jamrisko:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CMy only appeal is for the=
m to settle this deal with Malaysia because 1MDB is known throughout the wo=
rld,=E2=80=9D Anwar said Monday in Singapore. =E2=80=9CIt is there in the b=
ooks and I think that Goldman Sachs should come out clean and deal with Mal=
aysia.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Obviously the answer to that is that you go ou=
t and get some third-party bids on the yachts and give the arbitration pane=
l good evidence of valuation, but it is not a perfect answer.</p>
